{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-plugin-page-load-delay","description":"A Gatsby plugin to delay page loading.","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin","page","animation","delay"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"ken85rose","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/0dec49a05d40eddd3827688a1ad9680b"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/escaladesports/gatsby-plugin-page-load-delay"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-plugin-page-load-delay\"><a href=\"#gatsby-plugin-page-load-delay\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-plugin-page-load-delay</h1>\n<p>A Gatsby plugin to delay page loading. Useful for doing things like custom page animations.</p>\n<h2 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h2>\n<p>With Yarn:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\">\n      <pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">yarn add gatsby-plugin-page-load-delay</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>Or with npm:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\">\n      <pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> --save gatsby-plugin-page-load-delay</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h2 id=\"usage\"><a href=\"#usage\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// In your gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n\t<span class=\"token string\">'gatsby-plugin-page-load-delay'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>Set a window.pageExitTime variable in milliseconds to whatever you want the delay for that page to be.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// some-component.js</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">MyPage</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Component</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token function\">constructor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>props<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">super</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>props<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t<span class=\"token function\">componentDidMount</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">// Set delay in milliseconds</span>\n\t\twindow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pageExitTime <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1000</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t<span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">// A \"status\" property will be added</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">// You can use this to set classes, or trigger animations however you want</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>section className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>props<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>status<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t\t\tAnimation status<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>props<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>status<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>section<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>","timeToRead":1}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-plugin-page-load-delay/","id":"53274caa-494e-5130-b66a-60e26bd252dc"}}